<div class="col-lg-4">
	<div class="panel panel-primary">
	  <div class="panel-heading">
	    <h3 class="panel-title">3. Share</h3>
	  </div>
	  <div class="panel-body">
			<p>Kickstarter mixtape Vice XOXO, slow-carb vegan organic cray Thundercats tofu Williamsburg before they sold out.</p>
			<button type="button" class="col-lg-offset-5 col-lg-7 btn btn-success" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#upload_modal">
				Upload
			</button>
			<p>Crucifix roof party swag retro master cleanse wolf, polaroid sustainable mixtape Tumblr.</p>
			<button type="button" class="col-lg-offset-5 col-lg-7 btn btn-warning" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#tip_modal">
